title: CORRECTION FROM SOURCE: CSE: 2015-0813 - Fundamental Change - Scavo Resource Inc/Brabeia Inc
text:
August 27, 2015 16:44 ET CORRECTION FROM SOURCE: CSE: 2015-0813 - Fundamental Change - Scavo Resource Inc/Brabeia Inc 
TORONTO, ONTARIO--(Marketwired - Aug. 27, 2015) - Pursuant to a Fundamental Change Review, Brabeia Inc., the issuer resulting from a Fundamental Change of Scavo Resource Inc., has been approved for listing. 
Listing and disclosure documents will be available at thecse.com 
The symbol SCV will be delisted at the close on August 27, 2015. Brabeia Inc. will begin trading on August 28, 2015. New Listing: Brabeia Inc. Trading Date: August 28, 2015 New Symbol: BBA New CUSIP: 10373U 10 1 New ISIN: CA 10373U 10 1 2 Contact Information
